ts of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/88833/', '', 'Tocainide, Moricizine, Bretylium', '', 1767369485);
